**Learning vim**

Some most useful resources:

* Run [[tips/vimtutor]] first!
* Watch Derek Wyatt's [[http://www.derekwyatt.org/vim/vim-tutorial-videos/|awesome videos]]!
* Learn how to use the [[tips/using-vims-help]] command

